text: Rountzenheim-Auenheim is a commune. It is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Rountzenheim (the seat) and Auenheim.Arrêté préfectoral 4 September 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Bas-Rhin
